                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Success Metrics</h4>
                <ul class="text-secondary/90 leading-relaxed text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li>• <span class="font-semibold">Market expansion:</span> Scout captures <span class="font-semibold">untapped segments</span> (renters, students, outdoor enthusiasts)</li>
                  <li>• <span class="font-semibold">Conversion rate:</span> <span class="font-semibold">Scout-to-Charlie upgrades</span> vs. industry gateway product benchmarks</li>
                  <li>• <span class="font-semibold">Ecosystem engagement:</span> <span class="font-semibold">% of Scout+Charlie owners</span> actively using both products</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-32">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-4">Copper alternatives that could be added to further create an <span class="bg-yellow-100 px-1 rounded">integrated ecosystem</span>. 
                </h3>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
                  <div class="physics-block bg-secondary/5 p-6 rounded-lg cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing transition-all duration-200" data-block-id="spike">
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-start">
                      <div class="flex-1">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mb-1">Charlie Probe - "Spike"</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg text-secondary/80 mb-2">Wireless Culinary Thermometer</p>
